query:
INSERT INTO lend_storage (
                    fid,
                    to_fid,
                    num_units,
                    unit_type,
                    hash,
                    timestamp,
                    deleted_at
                )
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, NULL)
                ON CONFLICT (hash) DO UPDATE SET
                    deleted_at = NULL,
                    timestamp = LEAST(EXCLUDED.timestamp, lend_storage.timestamp)
